---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';

const locale = 'en';
const lastUpdated = 'March 9, 2026';
---

<MainLayout locale={locale} title="FinDIT | Privacy Policy">
  <article class="legal-shell">
    <header>
      <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="legal-meta">Last updated: {lastUpdated}</p>
    </header>

    <p class="legal-intro">
      This Privacy Policy explains what information FinDIT collects, how we use it, and how you can contact us.
      FinDIT is currently operated by an independent product team and is not yet registered as a legal company
      entity.
    </p>

    <div class="legal-body">
      <section>
        <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Waitlist information you submit, including email and page language (such as <code>en</code> or <code>zh</code>).</li>
          <li>Optional form details you provide voluntarily, such as name, role, and use case.</li>
          <li>Basic technical logs (for example IP, browser, and request metadata) used for security and abuse prevention.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>2. How We Use Information</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>To manage waitlist access, onboarding communication, and product updates.</li>
          <li>To send language-matched emails and reduce irrelevant communication.</li>
          <li>To operate, maintain, and secure FinDIT services.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>3. Processors and Infrastructure</h2>
        <p>We use third-party service providers to run core workflows, including:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Supabase for operational data storage.</li>
          <li>Resend for contact management and email delivery.</li>
          <li>Hosting platforms used to deliver the website.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>4. Data Retention</h2>
        <p>
          We keep waitlist and communication records only as long as necessary for product operations, security,
          compliance, and legitimate business needs. We may delete or anonymize records when they are no longer needed.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>5. Your Choices</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>You can request access, correction, or deletion of your waitlist data.</li>
          <li>You can unsubscribe from email updates at any time through the link in our emails.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>6. Children</h2>
        <p>
          FinDIT is not directed to children under 13, and we do not knowingly collect personal data from children under 13.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>7. Changes to This Policy</h2>
        <p>
          We may update this Privacy Policy as our product and infrastructure evolve. The latest version will always be
          posted on this page with an updated date.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>8. Contact</h2>
        <p>
          Questions about privacy or data handling can be sent to <a href="mailto:support@findit.studio">support@findit.studio</a>.
        </p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </article>
</MainLayout>
